sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Repairer
    participant FE as Frontend (React)
    participant API as Backend API (FastAPI)
    participant AUTH as Auth Middleware
    participant AI as LLM Service
    participant EMB as Embedding Service
    participant VDB as Vector DB (Chroma)
    participant RDB as PostgreSQL

    Repairer->>FE: Open /report and fill Problem, Cause, Solution, machine_type
    FE->>API: POST /reports/reformulate
    API->>AUTH: Validate token and user context
    AUTH-->>API: user + allowed_machines
    API->>API: Check machine_type in allowed_machines

    alt Unauthorized machine
        API-->>FE: 403 Forbidden
        FE-->>Repairer: Show access denied message
    else Authorized
        API->>AI: Reformulate structured fields
        AI-->>API: clean_problem, clean_cause, clean_solution
        API-->>FE: Return clean fields for review

        loop Until user approves
            alt User requests change
                Repairer->>FE: "Modify this report"
                FE->>API: POST /reports/modify (clean fields + instruction)
                API->>AI: Apply instruction to clean fields
                AI-->>API: Updated clean fields
                API-->>FE: Updated reformulated report
            else User approves
                Repairer->>FE: Approve
                FE->>API: POST /reports/commit
                API->>API: Build combined_clean_text
                API->>EMB: Generate embedding
                EMB-->>API: Embedding vector
                API->>VDB: Store vector + metadata
                API->>RDB: Store report metadata + references
                API-->>FE: 201 Created + report_id
                FE-->>Repairer: Confirmation message
            end
        end
    end
